$ forward Guard Dog Problem
$ assign dogs to guards, so that at least the target number share names
given n : int $ number of guards
given k : int $ number of dogs
given d : int $ target number of shared names
find f : function (bijective) int(1..n) --> int(1..k)
such that d <= sum i : int(1..k) . toInt(preImage(f, i) = {i})
$find f : function (total, injective) int(1..20) --> int(1..100)
$such that 7 = sum i : int(1..20) . toInt(f(i) = i)

